{
  "stem": "7598.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So both my uncle and ourselves were saved.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] Another little anecdote I'd like to bring-- to talk about is we, my brother and I, had some diamonds in our purse.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know how much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And wherever we were, they said, anything to declare, well, they used to frisk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We said, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the same thing happened when we landed in Bristol.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, do you have anything?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We said no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after a few days, or when we arrived, we took the little parcel and gave it to my father and it was, I suppose, worth quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father suddenly had a problem with the income tax people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, suddenly he's got sort of extra money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he thought, well, the only thing you could do is go and tell them the truth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he went and he said, my children just arrived and suddenly I've got a little capital, X, Y, Z.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were extremely nice about it and accepted what he said.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it was very strange, because suddenly he would have, you know, had-- he then had enough money to start to work on his own.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they might have said, well, where did you get this capital?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the beauty was that how honest and trustworthy the British were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I suppose they knew who to trust and not to trust.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- we have only come across kindness from the British.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know that they should have bombed the lines to the concentration camps in 1943.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were foreign ministers who said, why should we fight a war to save the children of our enemies, et cetera, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
